reduce its severity from "informational" to "debug".

Signed-off-by: Bart Van Assche <bart.vanassche@wdc.com>
Signed-off-by: Doug Ledford <dledford@redhat.com>
Acked-by: Thomas Bogendoerfer <tbogendoerfer@suse.de>
